            "Treasury narrative broadening 2025-07-29    609     285       -0.848412     0.000623         0.391858      0.614514                    1.408683                 0.076558        9.923577    7.395037e-08     \n",
            "\n",
            "=== Rolling(180d) stake_yield coefficient reversal check ===\n",
            "{'first_sustained_positive_date': '2025-10-28', 'sustain_windows': 20, 'last_coef': 2.1036470700237833, 'last_coef_ma30': 2.291325167821986}\n"
